326
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:38,160
Market crashes aren't random,

327
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:40,500
they follow predictable cycles.

328
00:11:40,500 --> 00:11:42,420
There are three types of crashes.

329
00:11:42,420 --> 00:11:45,690
Corrections, which is a 10% to 20% drop.

330
00:11:45,690 --> 00:11:46,920
These happen frequently

331
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:49,350
and are part of a healthy market.

332
00:11:49,350 --> 00:11:52,920
Bear markets, which is a 20% to 40% drop.

333
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:54,630
These happen every few years

334
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:57,900
and last about 289 days on average.

335
00:11:57,900 --> 00:11:59,190
And full collapses,

336
00:11:59,190 --> 00:12:01,440
which are more than 40% drops.

337
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,430
These are rare,

338
00:12:02,430 --> 00:12:03,960
but have historically been followed

339
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:06,150
by huge recoveries in the USA.

340
00:12:06,150 --> 00:12:08,400
The biggest mistake new investors make

341
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:11,220
