344
00:12:15,330 --> 00:12:18,030
When stocks rise, greed takes over,

345
00:12:18,030 --> 00:12:20,490
and then they buy at inflated prices.

346
00:12:20,490 --> 00:12:23,460
This cycle is why most
people fail at investing.

347
00:12:23,460 --> 00:12:25,530
So if you're already investing,

348
00:12:25,530 --> 00:12:28,380
